{"tid":576525,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"冇份開危機會議 雲加：命運非我自決","createTime":"2018-03-01T03:39:50.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-01T07:18:59.000Z","uid":94771,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"584cdeba62d6fda842ba2a260f7c1742a1d615c9","tid":576525,"uid":94771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-01T03:39:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://images-sports.now.com/sport/news/5/265/20549152265/20552634317_600x399.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages-sports.now.com%2Fsport%2Fnews%2F5%2F265%2F20549152265%2F20552634317_600x399.jpg&h=5ceddb62&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=yHZ6qo3DXskkgu8vni9lujANphTrK3OAdhrcB0lChBw%3D&h=4131547a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】英國傳媒報道阿仙奴隊長梅迪薩卡與隊友開危機會議，無份參與的領隊雲加坦言未來不在自己控制之内。<br />\n<br />\n阿仙奴周四在英超主場對曼城，賽前有關領隊雲加帥位呈危機的消息繼續發酵，《太陽報》更指隊長梅迪薩卡（Per Mertesacker）在聯賽盃決賽不敵曼城後召開危機會議，而領隊雲加卻沒參與之列。據悉，會議氣氛火爆，隊友互相指摘，梅迪薩卡則呼籲大家放下歧見，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">一起拯救雲加</span></span></strong>。<br />\n<br />\n梅迪薩卡季後將退役，擔任阿仙奴青年軍領隊，雲加合約則在下季期滿。該法國領隊被問到當前陣營狀況及其帥位問題時，他坦言將來已不在自己控制之中，他說：「你呢？你也不能決定在報館的將來吧？我跟你沒有分別。我是個打工仔，為深愛的球隊付出一切。」<br />\n<br />\n雲加還提到在阿仙奴21年一直尊重合約，「人生路上，我會看人們怎麼做，而不是怎麼說。當你問我的將來，那應該看我過去的事跡，而不是我在記者會上的言論。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://sports.now.com/home/news/details?id=20549152265\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsports.now.com%2Fhome%2Fnews%2Fdetails%3Fid%3D20549152265&d=yHZ6qo3DXskkgu8vni9lujANphTrK3OAdhrcB0lChBw%3D&h=6e4b1bdf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://sports.now.com/home/news/details?id=20549152265</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n爺爺加油，我想信你可以永續阿仙奴<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n永續雲加<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  永續雲加<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  永續雲加<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01f194dfdc59682eb0a3b78b4f6b0123a6be11ec","tid":576525,"uid":14075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-01T05:09:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2edb884259a2cd0448b2422dd3668e026550d00c","tid":576525,"uid":53238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-01T05:34:58.000Z","msg":"爺爺是無辜的"},{"pid":"59628aa681a4f585fd618167a6c80d70f59ed20d","tid":576525,"uid":35730,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-01T05:37:05.000Z","msg":"梅毒原來係最大迷雲黨"},{"pid":"6163ebb5e46cf2453f0f4f6970e36827499b7db2","tid":576525,"uid":19126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-01T05:38:32.000Z","msg":"永續爺爺啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57d375cb0dbff0f8a5af0d38d200bca76fd4aa82","tid":576525,"uid":4957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-01T05:39:55.000Z","msg":"阿仙唔配有雲加"},{"pid":"3f4bb044682089f0aa1a71d5e850e9a58f2871f2","tid":576525,"uid":61853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-01T05:46:54.000Z","msg":"無雲加就無阿仙奴<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff26e0c60dc13dc41c6a57389b350e6a0a70f098","tid":576525,"uid":94771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-01T06:54:27.000Z","msg":"爺爺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c1b51e305ef3d029b4106671a65014168ae06c7","tid":576525,"uid":64131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-01T07:18:59.000Z","msg":"細梅幾時死"}]}